ConditionGroup-Input.description:
A group of filter conditions combined with AND logic.

Used within SegmentFilters to create OR logic between groups.

Example:
    {"conditions": [
        {"field": "country", "operator": "eq", "value": "ES"},
        {"field": "device_type", "operator": "eq", "value": "mobile"}
    ]}

This generates: (country = 'ES' AND device_type = 'mobile')

ConditionGroup-Output.description:
A group of filter conditions combined with AND logic.

Used within SegmentFilters to create OR logic between groups.

Example:
