        {"field": "country", "operator": "eq", "value": "ES"},
        {"field": "device_type", "operator": "eq", "value": "mobile"}
    ]}

This generates: (country = 'ES' AND device_type = 'mobile')

FilterCondition.description:
A single filter condition within a segment.

Examples:
    {"field": "utm_medium", "operator": "eq", "value": "cpc"}
    {"field": "country", "operator": "in", "value": ["ES", "FR", "DE"]}
    {"field": "path", "operator": "starts_with", "value": "/blog"}

PixelProperty-Input.description:
A custom property for the pixel.

Example:
    {"key": "brand", "value": {"type": "gtm", "value": "{{product_brand}}"}}

PixelProperty-Output.description:
A custom property for the pixel.

Example:
    {"key": "brand", "value": {"type": "gtm", "value": "{{product_brand}}"}}

PixelValue.description:
A value in pixel configuration with type information.

Examples:
    {"type": "literal", "value": "EUR"}
    {"type": "gtm", "value": "{{order_total}}"}
    {"type": "js", "value": "window.productBrand"}

SegmentFilters-Input.description:
Collection of filter conditions for a segment.

Supports three modes:
1. Simple mode (backwards compatible): Use 'conditions' field directly.
   All conditions are combined with AND logic.

2. Advanced mode: Use 'groups' field with multiple condition groups.
   Conditions within each group are combined with AND.
   Groups are combined with OR logic.

3. Exclusion mode: Use 'not_groups' to exclude matching records.
   Each not_group is negated with NOT and combined with AND.

Examples:
    Simple (AND only):
    {"conditions": [
        {"field": "country", "operator": "eq", "value": "ES"},
        {"field": "device_type", "operator": "eq", "value": "mobile"}
    ]}
    -> (country = 'ES' AND device_type = 'mobile')

    Advanced (OR between groups):
    {"groups": [
        {"conditions": [{"field": "country", "operator": "eq", "value": "ES"}]},
        {"conditions": [{"field": "country", "operator": "eq", "value": "FR"}]}
    ]}
    -> (country = 'ES') OR (country = 'FR')

    Complex (AND within groups, OR between):
    {"groups": [
        {"conditions": [
            {"field": "country", "operator": "eq", "value": "ES"},
            {"field": "device_type", "operator": "eq", "value": "mobile"}
        ]},
        {"conditions": [
            {"field": "country", "operator": "eq", "value": "FR"},
            {"field": "device_type", "operator": "eq", "value": "desktop"}
        ]}
    ]}
    -> (country = 'ES' AND device_type = 'mobile') OR (country = 'FR' AND device_type = 'desktop')

    With NOT groups (exclusions):
    {"conditions": [
        {"field": "country", "operator": "eq", "value": "ES"}
    ],
    "not_groups": [
        {"conditions": [{"field": "utm_source", "operator": "eq", "value": "spam"}]},
        {"conditions": [{"field": "utm_source", "operator": "eq", "value": "bot"}]}
    ]}
    -> country = 'ES' AND NOT (utm_source = 'spam') AND NOT (utm_source = 'bot')

    Combined OR and NOT:
    {"groups": [
        {"conditions": [{"field": "country", "operator": "eq", "value": "ES"}]},
        {"conditions": [{"field": "country", "operator": "eq", "value": "FR"}]}
    ],
    "not_groups": [
        {"conditions": [{"field": "device_type", "operator": "eq", "value": "tablet"}]}
    ]}
    -> ((country = 'ES') OR (country = 'FR')) AND NOT (device_type = 'tablet')

